nl_querry: How many bonds are created by bonding atoms with chlorine element? chlorine refers to element = 'cl'
llm_querry: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.bond_id) FROM bond AS T1 JOIN atom AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id WHERE T2.element = 'cl'
gold_querry: SELECT COUNT(T1.bond_id) FROM connected AS T1 INNER JOIN atom AS T2 ON T1.atom_id = T2.atom_id WHERE T2.element = 'cl'
